<div text="#000000" bgcolor="#ffffff">Hi Hiral,<br><br>1.3.4 is quite old, please use the latest version. As Damien noted, the full fortran support is in 1.5 series, it&#39;s only experimental in 1.4 series. And there is only F77 bingdings on Windows, no F90 bindings. Another choice is to use the released binary installers to avoid compiling everything by yourself.<br>
<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Shiqing 
